The paper deals with natural language processing and specifically with improving the performance of neural machine translation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses techniques from the word sense disambiguation literature, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of context-aware word embeddings also suggests that the paper may fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses experiments on language pairs, which suggests that it may also fall under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) which often deals with language translation tasks.
